{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:1","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les devoirs des \u00e9v\u00eaques et des diacres<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. Tit 1:5-9. 1 Pi 5:1-4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Cette parole est certaine: Si quelqu\u2019un aspire \u00e0 la charge d\u2019\u00e9v\u00eaque, il d\u00e9sire une \u0153uvre excellente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il faut donc que l\u2019\u00e9v\u00eaque soit irr\u00e9prochable, mari d\u2019une seule femme, sobre, mod\u00e9r\u00e9, r\u00e9gl\u00e9 dans sa conduite, hospitalier, propre \u00e0 l\u2019enseignement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il faut qu\u2019il ne soit ni adonn\u00e9 au vin, ni violent, mais indulgent, pacifique, d\u00e9sint\u00e9ress\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il faut qu\u2019il dirige bien sa propre maison, et qu\u2019il tienne ses enfants dans la soumission et dans une parfaite honn\u00eatet\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>car si quelqu\u2019un ne sait pas diriger sa propre maison, comment prendra-t-il soin de l\u2019\u00c9glise de Dieu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il ne faut pas qu\u2019il soit un nouveau converti, de peur qu\u2019enfl\u00e9 d\u2019orgueil il ne tombe sous le jugement du diable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il faut aussi qu\u2019il re\u00e7oive un bon t\u00e9moignage de ceux du dehors, afin de ne pas tomber dans l\u2019opprobre et dans les pi\u00e8ges du diable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-13: cf. Ac 6:1-6. 1 Co 4:2.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\n    Les diacres aussi doivent \u00eatre honn\u00eates, \u00e9loign\u00e9s de la duplicit\u00e9, des exc\u00e8s du vin, d\u2019un gain sordide,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>conservant le myst\u00e8re de la foi dans une conscience pure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Qu\u2019on les \u00e9prouve d\u2019abord, et qu\u2019ils exercent ensuite leur minist\u00e8re, s\u2019ils sont sans reproche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Les femmes, de m\u00eame, doivent \u00eatre honn\u00eates, non m\u00e9disantes, sobres, fid\u00e8les en toutes choses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Les diacres doivent \u00eatre maris d\u2019une seule femme, et diriger bien leurs enfants et leurs propres maisons;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>car ceux qui remplissent convenablement leur minist\u00e8re s\u2019acqui\u00e8rent un rang honorable, et une grande assurance dans la foi en J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-16: cf. \u00c9p 2:19-22. (Jn 1:1, 14. Ro 1:4; 16:25, 26.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Je t\u2019\u00e9cris ces choses, avec l\u2019esp\u00e9rance d\u2019aller bient\u00f4t vers toi,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>mais afin que tu saches, si je tarde, comment il faut se conduire dans la maison de Dieu, qui est l\u2019\u00c9glise du Dieu vivant, la colonne et l\u2019appui de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.16","label":"","reference":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:16","prev_osis_id":"1Tim.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Tim.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et, sans contredit, le myst\u00e8re de la pi\u00e9t\u00e9 est grand: celui qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 manifest\u00e9 en chair, justifi\u00e9 par l\u2019Esprit, vu des anges, pr\u00each\u00e9 aux Gentils, cru dans le monde, \u00e9lev\u00e9 dans la gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbb8609f2.29597452');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb8609f2.29597452\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbb8609f2.29597452","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbb8609f2.29597452'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbb8609f2.29597452\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}